page.title: 05GARSWOOD FOOTBALL CLUB
page.content: The football club was formed in 1967.There are about eleven people in charge. The teams play at different grounds but mostly at Garswood Road. The football club is better than any other pub or club in Garswood. They have showers, changing rooms, toilets, club house, pitch, training area and car parks. The improvements are toilets and a better fence around the car park.{Garswood }is a much quieter village in{1985.}There have been no trophies won recently. There are a lot of players who have gone on to play professional football. Garswood have 3 football teams and they play in two leagues. The team train on Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday at 6 p.m. In the club they have{250}members. It is a very successful club.
